    {
      "id": "69ef72c10000000000543d9e",
      "text": "[atohs.icon]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777300161,
      "updated": 1777300170
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef72ca0000000000543da1",
      "text": "　「花見」の「花」って「桜」だよね、と説明することが多いです",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777300170,
      "updated": 1777300190
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef72dd0000000000543da2",
      "text": "　\t上位概念で下位概念を指す例",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777300190,
      "updated": 1777300203
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef72eb0000000000543da3",
      "text": "　「ご飯」で「食事」を指すことがあるよね、という例もよく使います",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777300203,
      "updated": 1777300218
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef72fa0000000000543da4",
      "text": "　\t下位概念で上位概念を指す例",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777300218,
      "updated": 1777300223
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef73020000000000543da5",
      "text": "　なお、隣接する概念で指し示すのは[換喩]と呼びます",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777300226,
      "updated": 1777300253
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef731d0000000000543da8",
      "text": "　[認知言語学]でよく使われるイメージ",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777300253,
      "updated": 1777300262
